description: Our favorite couple is back, and Derick stopped by to take advantage of the great Wyoming scenery and a couple of tight asses! On a chilly day, dipping into a hot tub is definitely a good idea to relax and warm up, but Derick, Deacon and Asher didn’t waste any time getting right to the fun stuff. Hot tub threesome with three very hot guys? You can’t go wrong with that!
title: Wyoming Getaway: Part 2
